sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Agents as My Agents / Wizard
    participant Picker as AgentTemplatePicker
    participant IPC as tauri.ts wrappers
    participant Rust as Tauri commands
    participant Catalog as Bundled template catalog
    participant Import as Existing import/create helpers
    participant FS as OpenClaw workspace/config

    User->>Agents: Click "Browse templates" or "Start from template"
    Agents->>Picker: Open picker
    Picker->>IPC: listAgentTemplates()
    IPC->>Rust: list_agent_templates
    Rust->>Catalog: Load manifest + validate templates
    Catalog-->>Rust: Template summaries
    Rust-->>IPC: Template summaries
    IPC-->>Picker: Cards + metadata
    Picker-->>User: Preview 10 starter agents

    User->>Picker: Choose template + confirm import
    Picker->>IPC: importAgentTemplate(templateId, targetName?)
    IPC->>Rust: import_agent_template
    Rust->>Catalog: Read selected template assets
    Rust->>Import: Reuse create/import pipeline
    Import->>FS: Write agent config + SOUL/IDENTITY/USER + skills
    FS-->>Import: Success
    Import-->>Rust: AgentDisplay
    Rust-->>IPC: Created agent
    IPC-->>Picker: Success response
    Picker->>Agents: Close + refresh agents list
    Agents-->>User: New template agent visible in My Agents
